	# Curate.it

	I made Curate.it between late 2011 to early 2012. It was one of my school projects. The concept was simple — an iPad photography magazine where people can easily browse and bookmark the content they like.

	Photographers would sign up and submit their projects. A curator would determine which ones to publish. Both the photographer and the curator would use the website to achieve those goals.

