	This project spaned over three semesters. With each exploration I gained more clarity and direction. If anything, this is what I learned: 

	+ Keep scope small. Do one thing well, not ten thing average. 
	+ Focus on content. 
	+ Make it for web, tailor content for mobile devices later.  
	+ Show progress often. Ask for feedback. 
	+ Choose a subject you are passionate about. 
	+ As a student, this might be one of the few opportunities where you get total freedom and all of your day time on a project.
	+ Have fun with it.   

